INE: </div><div class="t m2e7 x29 h27 y1cd9 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I. </div><div class="t m1c7d x66 h27 y1cd9 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Controversy with Israel (Hosea 4:1, 2). </div><div class="t mc6b x61 h27 y18df ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">II. </div><div class="t m2f6 x66 h27 y18df ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Prophet Introduced (Hosea 1:1, 2). </div><div class="t mbb2 x73 h27 ydcb ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">III. </div><div class="t m1347 x66 h27 ydcb ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Hosea&apos;s Message (Hosea 1:1, 2, 4, 6, 9). </div><div class="t mb5 x74 h27 y637 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">IV. </div><div class="t m1169 x66 h27 y637 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Prophet Takes a Wife (Hosea 1:2-9). </div><div class="t m1581 x26 h6d y1c2f ff1 fs12 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Second Lesson: </div><div class="t m67c x26 h87 y11ad ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;TWO HAZARDS TO A HAPPY HOME&quot; </div><div class="t m563 x74 h27 y1c31 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MEMORY TEXT: Phil. 2:3. </div><div class="t m1128 x74 h27 y1a29 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THIS WEEK&apos;S STUDY: Hosea 2:1-6. </div><div class="t med9 x74 h27 y1056 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">CENTRAL THOUGHT: There are many hazards to happy homes. </div><div class="t m673 x26 h27 y1370 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Two that are common and destructive in their efforts upon marital peace </div><div class="t m1abf x26 h27 yb83 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and prosperity are selfishness and lack of commitment. </div><div class="t m117b x74 h27 y1372 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">OUTLINE: </div><div class="t m2e7 x28 h27 y118f ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I. </div><div class="t m191a x5b h27 y118f ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Selfishness—Roots of Problems, Unhappiness, and Sin. </div><div class="t mc6b x29 h27 y1223 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">II. </div><div class="t m2f8 x5b h27 y1223 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lack of Commitment—Pitfall of Relationships. </div><div class="t m263 x18 h6d y1b92 ff1 fs12 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lessons On Evanne: </div><div class="t m67